9c2fee71-5ad7-4ebd-9d2f-7c9723b9dfbf.title: Legends guard
9c2fee71-5ad7-4ebd-9d2f-7c9723b9dfbf.text: Yes, how can I help you?

options.text: How do I get in here?
Can I speak to someone in charge?

ea25c1bf-2bcd-4e0a-825e-f0bc3a84707e.title: Legends guard
ea25c1bf-2bcd-4e0a-825e-f0bc3a84707e.text:
Legendary Gielinor citizens are invited on a quest in
order to become members of the guild.

options.text: Can I go on the quest?

07d16200-d8b9-4791-bcf0-74fdae340d01.title: <player>
07d16200-d8b9-4791-bcf0-74fdae340d01.text: Can I go on the quest?

66ea75b7-ee16-4275-b1bd-6d3fd4b16ab9.title: Legends guard
66ea75b7-ee16-4275-b1bd-6d3fd4b16ab9.text:
I'm very sorry but you need to complete more quests
before you can go on this quest. Additionally you need
to gain <point> more quest points. They don't call it the
Legends Guild for nothing you know!

options.text: Which quests do I need to complete?

57711266-ef43-4f2b-9467-08b95cc07b47.title: Legends guard
57711266-ef43-4f2b-9467-08b95cc07b47.text:
That's no problem... Best of luck if you intend to
become a member!

a7878fc8-f1b1-4338-b4ae-e5e67ab4dee8.title: Note
a7878fc8-f1b1-4338-b4ae-e5e67ab4dee8.text: Need dialogue for each quests required

358323f4-236d-4622-a92f-b24203752de6.title: <player>
358323f4-236d-4622-a92f-b24203752de6.text: How do I get in here?

7f9af9c2-4120-4672-bae4-32bab6740852.title: Legends guard
7f9af9c2-4120-4672-bae4-32bab6740852.text:
Well ma'am, you'll need to be a legendary citizen of
Gielinor.

d1e46a2d-e7e2-4449-9156-1c35afada319.title: Legends guard
d1e46a2d-e7e2-4449-9156-1c35afada319.text:
If you want to use the Legends Hall, you'll be invited
to complete a quest. Once you have completed that
quest, you'll be a fully fledged member of the Guild

options.text: Can I speak to someone in charge?

11ea26ef-7aa1-491f-8d06-746075c3fbb9.title: <player>
11ea26ef-7aa1-491f-8d06-746075c3fbb9.text: Can I speak to someone in charge?

039fc10d-1bb2-445e-9e40-5825449d3d9f.title: Legends guard
039fc10d-1bb2-445e-9e40-5825449d3d9f.text:
Well, Radimus Erkle is the Grand Vizier of the
Legends Guild. He's a very busy man. And he'll only
talk to those people eligible for the quest.
